OL,6,FThe Aberdulais Tinworks and Waterfall
OL,7,Fare have reopened after both were
OL,8,Ftemporarily closed due to Covid-19.
OL,10,FVisitors can explore over 400 years of
OL,11,Fhistory with free entry for everyone.
OL,13,FThroughout the centuries Aberdulais
OL,14,Fbecame a centre of industrial
OL,15,Fpioneering powered by water from the
OL,16,FAberdulais Falls.
