OL,3,CAberdulais Waterfall brought back to
OL,4,Clife after temporary closure
OL,6,FIt has been brought back to life after
OL,7,Fover 40 years of restoration and
OL,8,Fconservation work by National Trust
OL,9,FCymru since the organisation became
OL,10,Fcustodians in 1980.
OL,12,FLocated in the heart of the Neath
OL,13,FValley, Aberdulais is one of Britain's
OL,14,Fearliest industrial sites.
OL,16,FThe waterfall will be open to the
OL,17,Fpublic from 10:30am to 3.30pm on
OL,18,FThursdays and Fridays initially.
