OL,6,F"The completed restoration works
OL,7,Fensure that this gem of Welsh
OL,8,Findustrial history is here for
OL,9,Fgenerations to come.
OL,11,F"We look forward to welcoming people
OL,12,Ffrom the local community and further
OL,13,Fafield to enjoy Aberdulais, it's green
OL,14,Fspaces and historic past."
OL,16,FThe reopening marks the start of a new
